Aggrega i consensi di tutti i siti WordPress in un\'unica tabella.','Backend / Settings / Hint<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> tries to automatically detect domain and path.'=>'<translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> cerca di rilevare automaticamente il dominio e il percorso.','Backend / Settings / HintActivates <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> on your website. Displays the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and blocks iframes and other external media.'=>'Attiva <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> sul tuo sito web. Mostra la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> e blocca iframes e altri media esterni.','Backend / Settings / HintSpecify the domain scheme for which the cookie is valid. Example: If you enter <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> the cookie is also valid for subdomains like <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Specifica lo schema del dominio per il quale il cookie è valido. Esempio: se inserisci <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> il cookie è valido anche per sottodomini come <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintNumber of days until the visitor is asked again for their consent. Remember to adjust the <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Cookie Lifetime</translation-key> information of the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> under <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'Numero di giorni prima che al visitatore venga nuovamente chiesto il consenso. Ricordati di modificare le informazioni sulla <translation-key id="Cookie-Lifetime">Durata del cookie</translation-key> del <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> in <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintThe path for which the cookie is valid. Default path: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>'=>'Il percorso per il quale il cookie è valido. Percorso predefinito: <strong>{{ networkPath }}</strong>','Backend / Settings / HintThe <translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">SameSite attribute</translation-key> defines how the browser should handle cookies in cross-site requests. We recommend using the <strong>Lax</strong> option.'=>'L\'<translation-key id="SameSite-Attribute">Attributo SameSite</translation-key> definisce il modo in cui il browser deve gestire i cookie nelle richieste tra siti. Consigliamo di utilizzare l\'opzione <strong>Lax</strong>.','Backend / Settings / HintA cookie with the <translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Secure attribute</translation-key> is sent to the server only in case of an encrypted request via the HTTPS protocol.'=>'Un cookie con l\'<translation-key id="Secure-Attribute">Attributo Secure</translation-key> viene inviato al server solo in caso di richiesta crittografata tramite il protocollo HTTPS.','Backend / Settings / HintShows the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Increases with activating <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Update Cookie Version &amp; Force Re-Selection</translation-key>.'=>'Mostra la versione del cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Aumenta con l\'attivazione di <translation-key id="UpdateCookieVersionForceRe-Selection">Aggiornare la versione del cookie &amp; Forzare la riselezione</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintA bot/crawler is treated like a visitor who accepted all <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>.'=>'Un bot/crawler viene trattato come un visitatore che ha accettato tutti i <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintAdd one URL per line. Insert WordPress Address (URL). URL must end with <strong>/</strong>. Consent will be shared between websites.'=>'Aggiungi un URL per riga. Inserisci l\'indirizzo WordPress (URL). L\'URL deve terminare con <strong>/</strong>. I consensi saranno condivisi tra i siti web.','Backend / Settings / HintDisplay the <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> on the selected post types. The <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> allows you to add custom JavaScript on specific pages.'=>'Mostra il <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> sui tipi di articoli selezionati. Il <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> ti consente di aggiungere JavaScript personalizzato su pagine specifiche.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor saves their consent.'=>'Se abilitato, il sito web verrà ricaricato dopo che il visitatore avrà salvato il proprio consenso.','Backend / Settings / HintIf enabled, the website will be reloaded after the visitor opt out.'=>'Se abilitato, il sito web verrà ricaricato dopo l\'opt-out del visitatore.','Backend / Dialog Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Settings">Settings</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare tutte le <translation-key id="Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite.','Backend / Settings / HintA visitor with active <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Do Not Track&quot;</translation-key> setting will not see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> automatically selects the <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accept Only Essential</translation-key> option.'=>'Un visitatore con l\'impostazione <translation-key id="Do-Not-Track">&quot;Non tracciare&quot;</translation-key> attiva non vedrà la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> seleziona automaticamente l\'opzione <translation-key id="Accept-Only-Essential">Accetta solo i necessari</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / HintWith Setup Mode enabled, you can test your setup without having to enable <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>. Only you will see the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> on your website.'=>'Con la modalità configurazione attivata, puoi testare la tua configurazione senza dover abilitare lo <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Stato di Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Solo tu vedrai la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> sul tuo sito web.','Backend / Settings / HintUpdates the version of the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. This will cause the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> to reappear for visitors who have already selected an option.'=>'Aggiorna la versione del cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. In questo modo la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> riapparirà per i visitatori che hanno già selezionato un\'opzione.','Backend / Settings / TextVersion'=>'Versione','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you have to aggregate the consent:'=>'Quando è necessario aggregare il consenso:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using only the domain (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) and the other site a subdomain (e.g. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- se un sito utilizza solo il dominio (ad es. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong>) e l\'altro sito un sottodominio (ad es. <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if one site is using the root folder <strong>/</strong> and the other site a subfolder (e.g. <strong>/shop</strong>)'=>'- se un sito utilizza la cartella principale <strong>/</strong> e l\'altro sito una sottocartella (ad es. <strong>/shop</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextWhen you can separate the consent:'=>'Quando puoi separare il consenso:','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different domains (e.g. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) or different subdomains (e.g. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> and <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)'=>'- se tutti i siti utilizzano domini diversi (ad es. <strong><em>example.com</em></strong> e <strong><em>my-example.com</em></strong>) o sottodomini diversi (ad es. <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong> e <strong><em>shop.example.com</em></strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text- if all sites are using different subfolders (e.g. <strong>/en</strong> and <strong>/de</strong>)'=>'- se tutti i siti utilizzano sottocartelle diverse (ad es. <strong>/en</strong> e <strong>/de</strong>)','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe visitor\'s consent is transferred to all specified domains and WordPress installations, provided the websites are set up in the same way (<translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Service-Group">Service Group</translation-key> IDs must match). Any consent or modification by the visitor will be shared with the specified domains.'=>'Il consenso del visitatore viene trasferito a tutti i domini e alle installazioni WordPress specificate, a condizione che i siti web siano impostati allo stesso modo (<translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> e gli ID del <translation-key id="Service-Group">Gruppo di servizi</translation-key> devono combaciare). Qualsiasi consenso o modifica da parte del visitatore sarà condivisa con i domini specificati.','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Text<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>More information about <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>'=>'<a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Ulteriori informazioni su <translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cookie interdominio - Domini</translation-key></span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineAggregate Consents'=>'Aggregare i consensi','Backend / Settings / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cross Cookie Domains</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Cross-Cookie-Domains">Cookie interdominio - Domini</translation-key>','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Cookie Version?'=>'Che cos\'è la versione del cookie?','Backend / Settings / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the Meta Box?'=>'Che cos\'è il meta box?','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextThe cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> is assigned a version number. It is used to ask the visitor again for their consent if changes have been made to the <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key>. If the version number in the cookie differs from the current version number, the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> appears to the visitor.'=>'Al cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> viene assegnato un numero di versione. Viene utilizzato per chiedere nuovamente il consenso al visitatore se sono state apportate modifiche ai <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key>. Se il numero di versione del cookie è diverso da quello attuale, al visitatore viene mostrata la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Settings / Things to know / TextIf active the <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta Box</translation-key> is displayed in the selected post types. This allows you to execute code (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcodes</translation-key>) on the page and e.g. trigger a conversion pixel.'=>'Se attivo, il <translation-key id="Meta-Box">Meta box</translation-key> viene mostrato nei tipi di articoli selezionati. Ciò ti consente di eseguire codici (JavaScript, HTML, <translation-key id="Shortcodes">Shortcode</translation-key>) sulla pagina e, ad esempio, di attivare un pixel di conversione.','Backend / Settings / URLhttps://borlabs.io/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&amp;utm_medium=Footer+Logo&amp;utm_campaign=Analysis'=>'https://borlabs.io/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&amp;utm_medium=Footer+Logo&amp;utm_campaign=Analysis','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Script Blocker / Field LabelContent Blocker Global JavaScript'=>'Content blocker JavaScript Globale','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelHandles'=>'Handle','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelPhrases'=>'Frasi','Backend / Script Blocker / LabelService Opt-in Script Tag'=>'Tag script per l\'opt-in del servizio','Backend / Style Blocker / LabelStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Configuration'=>'Configurazione dello style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Information'=>'Informazioni sullo style blocker','Backend / Style Blocker / HeadlineStyle Blocker Settings'=>'Impostazioni dello style blocker','Backend / Script Blocker / HintIf your intention is to unblock previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> upon unblocking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, please insert the provided JavaScript into the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field within your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> settings.'=>'Se la tua intenzione è quella di sbloccare <translation-key id="Styles">Stili</translation-key> precedentemente bloccati al momento dello sblocco di un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, inserisci il JavaScript fornito nel campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> delle tue impostazioni del <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere impostato. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere lungo almeno 3 caratteri e può contenere solo: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Il nome dello <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blocker / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked <translation-key id="Styles">Styles</translation-key> through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Per consentire lo sblocco di <translation-key id="Styles">Stili</translation-key> precedentemente bloccati tramite il consenso dell\'utente per un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>, inserisci il seguente tag script nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> all\'interno del tuo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blocker / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block stylesheets and style-tags.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>. Se lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> è disattivato, non bloccherà i fogli di stile e i tag.','Backend / Style Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Non è stato configurato alcuno <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blockers / BreadcrumbStyle Blockers'=>'Style blocker','Backend / Style Blockers / HeadlineStyle Blockers'=>'Style blocker','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineHandles'=>'Handle','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlinePhrases'=>'Frasi','Backend / Style Blockers / Table HeadlineStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key>?','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / HeadlineLanguage independent'=>'Indipendente dalla lingua','Backend / Style Blockers / Tip / Text<translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> are configured independently for all languages.'=>'Gli <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key> sono configurati in modo indipendente per tutte le lingue.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style Blockers</translation-key> section allows you to block <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> from <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key> that, for example, embed <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> to load external fonts like <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.'=>'La sezione <translation-key id="Style-Blockers">Style blocker</translation-key> ti consente di bloccare <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> da <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugin</translation-key> che, ad esempio, incorporano <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> per caricare font esterni come <translation-key id="Google-Fonts">Google Fonts</translation-key>.','Backend / Style Blockers / Things to know / TextOnce a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is created, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Una volta creato uno <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fornisce un JavaScript di sblocco che può essere inserito nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> di un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Il <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> viene sbloccato una volta che il visitatore dà il suo consenso al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> è abilitato e impedisce attivamente l\'esecuzione dei <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> se le <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o le <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key> corrispondono a un termine configurato nel sistema.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>. Non disponibile per uno <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> installato tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Modifica lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> are executed without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Style-Blocker">Style blocker</translation-key> è inattivo e consente l\'esecuzione di tutti i <translation-key id="CSS">CSS</translation-key> senza filtri o restrizioni basate su <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key>.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageConnecting to the API failed. Please check that Wordpress has access to the Internet or retry later.'=>'La connessione all\'API è fallita. Verificare che Wordpress abbia accesso a Internet o riprovare più tardi.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageMoving the database file failed.'=>'Lo spostamento del file di database è fallito.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessagePlease enable GeoIP before downloading the database.'=>'Attivare il GeoIP prima di scaricare il database.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageThe database was successfully updated.'=>'Il database è stato aggiornato con successo.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageYou already have the most up-to-date database.'=>'Hai già il database più aggiornato.','Backend / GeoIp / Alert MessageUnpacking the database to the temporary folder failed. Please check if the temporary folder is writable and the PHP module ZIP is installed.'=>'La decompressione del database nella cartella temporanea non è riuscita. Verificare che la cartella temporanea sia scrivibile e che il modulo PHP ZIP sia installato.','Backend / Model Localization / ModelCompatibility Patch'=>'Patch di compatibilità','Backend / Model Localization / ModelContent Blocker'=>'Content blocker','Backend / Model Localization / ModelProvider'=>'Provider','Backend / Services / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Tracking">Tracking</translation-key> cookies are used to analyze user behavior on the website 