ers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Per motivi di conformità legale, ogni <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> deve essere collegato a un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> specifico.','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is the company that delivers the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> (e.g., Google Analytics) or the content (e.g., YouTube videos).'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> è la società che fornisce il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> (ad es. Google Analytics) o il contenuto (ad es. i video di YouTube).','Backend / Providers / Things to know / TextVisitors should receive clear information about the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsible for the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> or blocked content.'=>'I visitatori devono ricevere informazioni chiare sul <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> responsabile del <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> o del contenuto bloccato.','Backend / Providers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Providers / HeadlineProviders'=>'Provider','Backend / Providers / HeadlineReset Default Providers'=>'Ripristinare i provider predefiniti','Backend / Providers / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset the <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key>. They will be reset to their default