t-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Il nome dello <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintTo allow the unblocking of previously blocked JavaScripts through user consent for a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>, please insert the ensuing script tag into the field labeled <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> within your <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Per consentire lo sblocco di JavaScript precedentemente bloccati tramite il consenso dell\'utente per un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>, inserisci il tag script che segue nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> all\'interno del tuo <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. If the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is disabled, it will not block JavaScript.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>. Se lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è disattivato, non bloccherà JavaScript.','Backend / Script Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Non è stato configurato alcuno <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / HeadlineScript Blockers'=>'Script blocker','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key>','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Script Blockers / Table HeadlineName'=>'Nome','Backend / Script Blockers / Table Headline<translation-key id="On-Exist">OnExist</translation-key>'=>'<tra