lation-key> provides an unblock JavaScript that can be entered into the <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Opt-in Code</translation-key> field of a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>. The JavaScript becomes unblocked once a visitor consents to the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Una volta creato uno <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fornisce un JavaScript di sblocco che può essere inserito nel campo <translation-key id="Opt-in-Code">Codice opt-in</translation-key> di un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>. Il JavaScript viene sbloccato una volta che il visitatore dà il suo consenso al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Script Blockers / Things to know / TextThis usually allows you to continue using your favorite plugins, but their JavaScript will only run when a visitor gave consent.'=>'Questo di solito ti consente di continuare a utilizzare i tuoi plugin preferiti, ma il loro JavaScript verrà eseguito solo quando il visitatore ha dato il suo consenso.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is enabled and actively prevents JavaScript execution if the <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key> matches a term configured in the system.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è abilitato e impedisce attivamente l\'esecuzione di JavaScript se gli <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o le <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key> corrispondono a un termine configurato nel sistema.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextDelete the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>. Not available for a <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> installed via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'Elimina lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>. Non disponibile per uno <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> installato tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextEdit the <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Modificare lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script Blocker</translation-key> is inactive, allowing all JavaScript to execute without filtering or restricting based on <translation-key id="Handles">Handles</translation-key> or <translation-key id="Phrases">Phrases</translation-key>.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Script-Blocker">Script blocker</translation-key> è inattivo e consente l\'esecuzione di tutti i JavaScript senza filtri o restrizioni basate su <translation-key id="Handles">Handle</translation-key> o <translation-key id="Phrases">Frasi</translation-key>.','Backend / Service Cookie / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Cookie">Cookie</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Service Cookie / ButtonAdd Cookie'=>'Aggiungi un cookie','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldLifetime'=>'Durata','Backend / Service Cookie / FieldName'=>'Nome','Backend / Service Cookie / HeadlineCookies'=>'Cookie','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineDescription'=>'Descrizione','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineHostname'=>'Nome host','Backend / Service Cookie / Table HeadlineLifetime'=>'Durata','Backend / Service Cookie / Table Headline<translation-key id="Name">Name</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Name">Nome</