; <translation-key id="Navigation-Iab-Tcf-Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key></em>) l\'ingresso della finestra di dialogo mostrerà questi testi al posto dei testi <translation-key id="Legal-Information">Informazioni legali</translation-key>.','Backend / Country / CountryHaiti'=>'Haiti','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextThe dialog <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> inform about the topics: '=>'La finestra di dialogo <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">deve</span> informare sugli argomenti: ','Backend / Country / CountryHungary'=>'Ungheria','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextTexts <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> also distinguish between <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> (TCF Standard) and <translation-key id="Providers">Providers</translation-key> (Non-TCF Standard).'=>'I testi <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">devono</span> anche distinguere tra <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendor</translation-key> (Standard TCF) e <translation-key id="Providers">Provider</translation-key> (Standard Non-TCF).','Backend / Country / CountryIndonesia'=>'Indonesia','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">Warning</span>: Should your modifications infringe upon the IAB\'s TCF standards and we are alerted to a complaint from the IAB, your license will be irrevocably terminated without compensation.'=>'<span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">Attenzione</span>: se le tue modifiche dovessero violare gli standard TCF di IAB e noi fossimo avvisati di un reclamo da parte dello IAB, la tua licenza sarà irrevocabilmente interrotta senza alcun risarcimento.','Backend / Country / CountryIreland'=>'Irlanda','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextShould you harbor any uncertainties regarding the compliance of your proposed alterations with the TCF standard, we strongly encourage you to reach out to us prior to implementing any changes.'=>'Se dovessi nutrire incertezze riguardo alla conformità delle modifiche proposte con lo standard TCF, ti invitiamo vivamente a contattarci prima di implementare eventuali modifiche.','Backend / Country / CountryIsrael'=>'Israele','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Technology">Technology</translation-key>: The technologies used, for example: cookies and their purpose. The number of <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> also be mentioned with the help of <strong><em>{{ totalVendors }}</em></strong>.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Technology">Tecnologia</translation-key>: le tecnologie utilizzate, ad esempio i cookie e le loro finalità. Anche il numero di <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendor</translation-key> <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">deve</span> essere indicato con l\'aiuto di <strong><em>{{ totalVendors }}</em></strong>.','Backend / Country / CountryIsle of Man'=>'Isola di Man','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Personal-Data">Personal Data</translation-key>: What types of personal data are processed?'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Personal-Data">Dati personali</translation-key>: quali tipi di dati personali vengono trattati?','Backend / Country / CountryIndia'=>'India','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Legitimate-Interest">Legitimate Interest</translation-key>: You <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">must</span> inform about the legitimate interest that some <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> claim for data processing.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Legitimate-Interest">Interesse legittimo</translation-key>: <span class="brlbs-cmpnt-important-text">devi</span> informare circa l\'interesse legittimo che alcuni <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendor</translation-key> rivendicano per il trattamento dei dati.','Backend / Country / CountryBritish Indian Ocean Territory'=>'Territorio britannico dell\'Oceano Indiano','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-More-Information">More Information</translation-key>: Where the visitor can find more information about the <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> and the data processed.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-More-Information">Ulteriori informazioni</translation-key>: dove il visitatore può trovare ulteriori informazioni sui <translation-key id="Vendors">Vendor</translation-key> e sui dati trattati.','Backend / Country / CountryIraq'=>'Iraq','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-No-Commitment">No Commitment</translation-key>: That the visitor can visit the website without giving consent.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-No-Commitment">Senza impegno</translation-key>: che il visitatore può visitare il sito web senza dare il proprio consenso.','Backend / Country / CountryIran'=>'Iran','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Revoke">Revoke</translation-key>: That the visitor can revoke the consent any time.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Revoke">Revoca</translation-key>: che il visitatore può revocare il consenso in qualsiasi momento.','Backend / Country / CountryIceland'=>'Islanda','Backend / Dialog Localization / Text<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Individual-Settings">Individual Settings</translation-key>: That due to individual settings certain functionalities of the website may be unavailable or operate suboptimally.'=>'<translation-key id="Tcf-Topic-Individual-Settings">Impostazioni individuali</translation-key>: che a causa delle impostazioni individuali, alcune funzionalità del sito web potrebbero non essere disponibili o funzionare in modo non ottimale.','Backend / Country / CountryItaly'=>'Italia','Backend / Dialog Localization / TextYou can select which legal information topics you want to show to a visitor.'=>'Puoi selezionare gli argomenti di informazione legale da mostrare al v