 suggerito','Backend / Dashboard / Texthere'=>'qui','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableURL'=>'URL','Backend / Dashboard / TextIn memory of Sergii Kovalenko.'=>'In memoria di Sergii Kovalenko.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Textdays'=>'giorni','Backend / Dashboard / TextHelp us improve <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> by providing us with non-personal information about your website.'=>'Aiutaci a migliorare <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> fornendoci informazioni non personali sul tuo sito web.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextFailed'=>'Fallito','Backend / Dashboard / TextFor more information about what data we need and for what purpose, <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>click here</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.'=>'Per ulteriori informazioni sui dati di cui abbiamo bisogno e per quale finalità, <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>clicca qui</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextSuccess'=>'Successo','Backend / Dashboard / TextThe dialog should now appear on your website. Open your website in incognito/private mode for testing. If you have any questions, please visit our <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Knowledge Base</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.'=>'La finestra di dialogo dovrebbe ora apparire sul tuo sito web. Apri il tuo sito web in modalità incognito/privata per fare delle prove. Per qualsiasi domanda, visita la nostra <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link brlbs-cmpnt-link-with-icon" href="%s" rel="nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank"><span>Knowledge base</span><span class="brlbs-cmpnt-external-link-icon"></span></a>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScan in progress'=>'Scansione in corso','Backend / Dashboard / TextPlease disable your caching plugin if it is currently enabled. Once you have completed the setup of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>, you may re-enable it.'=>'Disattiva il plugin di cache se è attualmente abilitato. Una volta completata la configurazione di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>, puoi riattivarlo.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScan is analysing'=>'La scansione sta analizzando','Backend / Dashboard / TextUpdate the default provider data under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-provider"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Owner of this website</translation-key>. Please update the data by adding your name and address, and ensure to include the URL for the <translation-key id="Privacy-Url">Privacy URL</translation-key>.'=>'Aggiorna i dati del provider predefinito in <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-provider"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Provider</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Owner-of-this-website">Proprietario di questo sito web</translation-key>. Aggiorna i dati aggiungendo il tuo nome e indirizzo e assicurati di includere l\'URL per l\'<translation-key id="Privacy-Url">URL informativa sulla privacy</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextScanning'=>'In scansione','Backend / Dashboard / TextClick on <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a> and select your <translation-key id="Privacy-Page">Privacy Page</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Imprint-Page">Imprint Page</translation-key>. Add both pages to <translation-key id="Hide-Dialog-on-Pages">Hide Dialog on Pages</translation-key> too.'=>'Clicca su <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Finestra di dialogo &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key></a> e seleziona le pagine <translation-key id="Privacy-Page">Pagina dell\'informativa sulla privacy</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Imprint-Page">Pagina dell\'impressum</translation-key>. Aggiungi entrambe le pagine a <translation-key id="Hide-Dialog-on-Page">Nascondere la finestra di dialogo sulle pagine</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TextSession'=>'Sessione','Backend / Dashboard / TextEnable <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> under <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Borlabs Cookie Status</translation-key>.'=>'Attiva <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> sotto <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie-Status">Stato di Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertThe scanner\'s analysis can make suggestions for installing packages that prevent the inclusion of external resources or improve compatibility between the theme and installed plugins.'=>'L\'analisi dello scanner può suggerire di installare pacchetti che impediscano l\'inclusione di risorse esterne o migliorino la compatibilità tra il tema e i plugin installati.','Backend / Dashboard / TextUse our scanner to check which cookies are set on your website and which services are used. Click on <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-cloud-scan"><translation-key id="Navigation-Scanner">Scanner</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Add-New">Add New</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Create-Scan">Create scan</translation-key> to add a new scan job. The <translation-key id="Scan-type">Scan type</translation-key> should be set to <translation-key id="Setup">Setup</translation-key>. '=>'Utilizza il nostro scanner per verificare quali cookie sono impostati sul tuo sito web e quali servizi sono utilizzati. Clicca su <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-cloud-scan"><translation-key id="Navigation-Scanner">Scanner</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Add-New">Aggiungi nuovo</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Button-Create-Scan">Crea scansione</translation-key> per aggiungere un nuovo processo di scansione. Il <translation-key id="Scan-type">Tipo di scansione</translation-key> deve essere impostato su <translation-key id="Setup">Configurazione</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertClick on the <translation-key id="Button-Details">Details</translation-key> button to get more information about the package. Once the package is installed, you will be redirected back to this page to proceed with the installation of the next package.'=>'Clicca sul pulsante <translation-key id="Button-Details">Dettagli</translation-key> per ottenere ulteriori informazioni sul pacchetto. Una volta installato il pacchetto, verrai reindirizzato a questa pagina per procedere all\'installazione del pacchetto successivo.','Backend / Dashboard / TextAfter you have used the scanner and installed suggested packages, create a new scan job and set <translation-key id="Scan-type">Scan type</translation-key> to <translation-key id="Audit">Audit</translation-key>. This scan type is used to verify that your website does not load cookies or external resources without obtaining the appropriate consent.'=>'Dopo aver utilizzato lo scanner e installato i pacchetti suggeriti, crea un nuovo processo di scansione e imposta il <translation-key id="Scan-type">Tipo di scansione</translation-key> su <translation-key id="Audit">Audit</translation-key>. Questo tipo di scansione viene utilizzato per verificare che il tuo sito web non carichi cookie o risorse esterne senza aver ottenuto il consenso appropriato.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipTo comply with data protection, cookies must be blocked in most cases until consent is given. Only essential cookies may be set without consent. An essential cookie could be one that, for instance, stores the shopping cart contents or the selected language.'=>'Per rispettare la protezione dei dati, nella maggior parte dei casi i cookie devono essere bloccati fino a quando non viene dato il consenso. Solo i cookie necessari possono essere impostati senza consenso. Un cookie necessario può essere quello che, ad esempio, memorizza il contenuto del carrello della spesa o la lingua selezionata.','Backend / Dashboard / TextExplore our <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-library"><translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key></a> to have an overview of all our available packages. Here you can find templates for <translation-key id="Services">Services</translation-key> (e.g. Google Analytics) or <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> (e.g. YouTube) and much more.'=>'Esplora la nostra <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-library"><translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key></a> per avere una panoramica di tutti i nostri pacchetti disponibili. Qui puoi trovare modelli per <translation-key id="Services">Servizi</translation-key> (ad es. Google Analytics) o <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content blocker</translation-key> (ad es. YouTube) e molto altro ancora.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipClick the icon to view sample locations associated with the detected cookie.'=>'Clicca sull\'icona per visualizzare gli indirizzi di esempio associati al cookie rilevato.','Backend / Dashboard / TextIf you place ads on your website, you may need to enable the IAB TCF under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">IAB TCF Status</translation-key>. And then configure vendors under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">IAB TCF</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-vendor"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Manage-Vendors">Manage Vendors</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Configure-Vendors">Configure Vendors</translation-key>.'=>'Se pubblichi annunci sul tuo sito web, potrebbe essere necessario abilitare il TCF di IAB sotto <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">TCF di IAB</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Status">Stato del TCF di IAB</translation-key>. Poi configura i vendor sotto <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF">TCF di IAB</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-iab-tcf-vendor"><translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-IAB-TCF-Manage-Vendors">Gestione vendor</translation-key></a> &raquo; <translation-key id="Configure-Vendors">Configura i vendor</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Suggested package</translation-key>: This column lists a recommended package to install to block the cookie if the cookie is not essential.'=>'<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Pacchetto suggerito</translation-key>: questa colonna elenca un pacchetto consigliato da installare per bloccare il cookie se non è necessario.','Backend / Dashboard / TextYou can customize the dialog texts under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-localization"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Localization">Localization</translation-key></a>. The visual appearance (colors, spacing, etc.) can be customized under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-appearance"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Appearance">Appearance</translation-key></a>. Everything else like layout, position, buttons, etc. you can define under <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Dialog &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Dialog</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Settings</translation-key></a>.'=>'Puoi personalizzare i testi della finestra di dialogo sotto <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Finestra di dialogo &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-localization"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Localization">Localizzazione</translation-key></a>. L\'aspetto visivo (colori, spaziatura, ecc.) può essere personalizzato in <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Finestra di dialogo &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-appearance"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Appearance">Aspetto</translation-key></a>. Puoi definire tutto il resto, come il layout, la posizione, i pulsanti, ecc. in <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget">Finestra di dialogo &amp; Widget</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key> &raquo; <a class="brlbs-cmpnt-link" href="?page=borlabs-cookie-dialog-settings"><translation-key id="Navigation-Dialog-Widget-Dialog-Settings">Impostazioni</translation-key></a>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipCookies'=>'Cookie','Backend / Dashboard / TextThank you!'=>'Grazie!','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipExternal resources'=>'Risorse esterne','Backend / Dashboard / URLhttps://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/telemetry/'=>'https://borlabs.io/borlabs-cookie/telemetry/','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Dashboard / URLhttps://borlabs.io/support/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&utm_medium=Dashboard+Link&utm_campaign=Analysis'=>'https://borlabs.io/support/?utm_source=Borlabs+Cookie&utm_medium=Dashboard+Link&utm_campaign=Analysis','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipExternal resources are resources that are loaded from a different domain than the page itself. For example, if you have a page with the URL <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> and this page loads a resource from <strong><em>https://www.example.org</em></strong>, then this resource is considered an external resource. To comply with data protection, in most cases, these external resources must be blocked until consent is given.'=>'Le risorse esterne sono risorse caricate da un dominio diverso da quello della pagina stessa. Ad esempio, se hai una pagina con l\'URL <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong> e questa pagina carica una risorsa da <strong><em>https://www.example.org</em></strong>, questa risorsa è considerata una risorsa esterna. Per rispettare la protezione dei dati, nella maggior parte dei casi queste risorse esterne devono essere bloccate fino a quando non viene dato il consenso.','Seeder / Default Content Blocker / DescriptionThe <strong><em>Default</em> Content Blocker</strong> is a special type that is always used when no specific <strong>Content Blocker</strong> was found.<br>Therefore it is not possible to use the <strong>Unblock all</strong> feature.'=>'Il <strong>content blocker<em>predefinito</em></strong> è un tipo speciale che viene sempre usato quando non è stato trovato alcun <strong>content blocker</strong> specifico.<br>Pertanto non è possibile usare la funzione <strong>sblocca tutto</strong>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipClick on the icon to get detailed information about the external resource. In the details you can find examples of discovered resources and their respective locations.'=>'Clicca sull\'icona per ottenere informazioni dettagliate sulla risorsa esterna. Nei dettagli puoi trovare esempi di risorse rilevate e i rispettivi indirizzi.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="External-hostname">External hostname</translation-key>: Resources are being loaded from this source.'=>'<translation-key id="External-hostname">Nome host esterno</translation-key>: le risorse vengono caricate da questa fonte.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Number of resources</translation-key>: The number of resources loaded from this source. The resources found are limited to 10 per hostname.'=>'<translation-key id="Number-of-resources">Numero di risorse</translation-key>: il numero di risorse caricate da questa fonte. Le risorse trovate sono limitate a 10 per hostname.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Tip<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Suggested package</translation-key>: This column lists a recommended package to install to block the external resource.'=>'<translation-key id="Suggested-package">Pacchetto suggerito</translation-key>: questa colonna elenca un pacchetto consigliato da installare per bloccare la risorsa esterna.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipFailed: The scanner could not scan the page. More information can be found in the <translation-key id="Failure-type">Failure type</translation-key> column.'=>'Fallito: lo scanner non ha potuto acquisire la pagina. Ulteriori informazioni sono riportate nella colonna <translation-key id="Failure-type">Tipo di errore</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipSuccess: The page was scanned successfully.'=>'Successo: la pagina è stata scansionata con successo.','Backend / Cloud Scan / TipScanning: The page is being scanned.'=>'Scansione: la pagina è in fase di scansione.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertNo <translation-key id="Scans">Scans</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessuna <translation-key id="Scans">Scansione</translation-key> configurata.','Backend / Cloud Scan / HeadlineScanner'=>'Scanner','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableCloud Scan ID'=>'ID scansione cloud','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableCreated at'=>'Creato il','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableScanned pages'=>'Pagine scansionate','Backend / Cloud Scan / TableType'=>'Tipo','Backend / Cloud Scan / Things to know / TextThe scanner will help you set up <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> that will help you make your website privacy compliant. Two scan options are available for this purpose.'=>'Lo scanner ti aiuterà a impostare <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>, che ti aiuterà a rendere il tuo sito web conforme alla privacy. A tale scopo sono disponibili due opzioni di scansione.','Backend / Cloud Scan / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the functionality of the scanner?'=>'Qual è la funzionalità dello scanner?','Backend / Compatibility Patch Details / Alert MessageError: The required file is missing. To resolve this issue, please reinstall the package.'=>'Errore: il file richiesto è mancante. Per risolvere il problema, reinstallare il pacchetto.','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListCalculated Hash'=>'Hash calcolato','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListFile Name'=>'Nome del file','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListFile Path'=>'Percorso del file','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListID'=>'ID','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListInstalled at'=>'Installato il','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListPackage'=>'Pacchetto','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListRequired Hash'=>'Hash necessario','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListUpdated at'=>'Aggiornato il','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListValid'=>'Valido','Backend  / Compatibility Patch Details /  Description ListVersion'=>'Versione','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> configured.'=>'Non è stato configurato alcun <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key>.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / BreadcrumbCompatibility Patches'=>'Patch di compatibilità','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Headline<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key>','Backend / Compatibility Patches / PlaceholderSearch key or file name...'=>'Cerca la chiave o il nome del file...','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlinePackage'=>'Pacchetto','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineFile name'=>'Nome del file','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineHash'=>'Hash','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineID'=>'ID','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Table HeadlineValid'=>'Valido','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowClick on the icon to get detailed information about the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key>.'=>'Clicca sull\'icona per ottenere informazioni dettagliate sul <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key>.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key>?','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowThe file of the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> is invalid. Please reinstall the package via the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key> to resolve this issue.'=>'Il file del <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key> non è valido. Per risolvere il problema, reinstalla il pacchetto tramite la <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key>.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowIn this section, you can see all <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Compatibility Patches</translation-key> that have been installed by packages from the <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Library</translation-key>.'=>'In questa sezione puoi vedere tutti i <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patches">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key> che sono stati installati dai pacchetti della <translation-key id="Navigation-Library">Libreria</translation-key>.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowA <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> is used to enhance compatibility with other <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugins</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Themes">Themes</translation-key> external services.'=>'Un <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key> viene utilizzato per migliorare la compatibilità con altri <translation-key id="Plugins">Plugin</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Themes">Temi</translation-key> e servizi esterni.','Backend / Compatibility Patches / Things to knowThe file of the <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Compatibility Patch</translation-key> is valid.'=>'Il file del <translation-key id="Compatibility-Patch">Patch di compatibilità</translation-key> è valido.','Backend / Consent Log / Alert MessageThe <translation-key id="Consent-Log">Consent Log</translation-key> could not be found.'=>'Non è stato possibile trovare il <translation-key id="Consent-Log">Log di consenso</translation-key>.','Backend / Consent Log / Breadcrumb<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Log di consenso</translation-key>','Backend / Consent Log / BreadcrumbDetails'=>'Dettagli','Backend / Consent Log / FieldConsents'=>'Consensi','Backend / Consent Log / FieldCookie Version'=>'Versione del cookie','Backend / Consent Log / LabelIAB TCF TC String'=>'Stringa TC TCF di IAB','Backend / Consent Log / LabelIs Latest Consent'=>'È l\'ultimo consenso','Backend / Consent Log / LabelUID'=>'UID','Backend / Consent Log / HintA version number is assigned to the cookie of <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. It is used to ask the visitor for consent again when changes are made to the cookies. If the version number in the cookie differs from the current version number, the consent dialog appears to the visitor.'=>'Al cookie di <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key> viene assegnato un numero di versione. Viene utilizzato per chiedere nuovamente il consenso al visitatore quando vengono apportate modifiche ai cookie. Se il numero di versione del cookie differisce dal numero di versione attuale, la finestra di dialogo viene mostrata al visitatore per il consenso.','Backend / Consent Log / HintThe <translation-key id="TC-String">TC String</translation-key> is an encoded depiction of user consent choices, generated through interactions with <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. It informs publishers, advertisers, and ad tech vendors of the permitted uses of user data, based on users\' consent decisions.'=>'La <translation-key id="TC-String">Stringa TC</translation-key> è una rappresentazione codificata delle scelte di consenso degli utenti, generata attraverso le interazioni con <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>. Informa editori, inserzionisti e vendor di tecnologia pubblicitaria degli usi consentiti dei dati degli utenti, in base alle decisioni di consenso degli utenti.','Backend / Consent Log / HintThe <translation-key id="UID">UID</translation-key> is a unique identifier of the user, generated through interactions with <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.'=>'L\'<translation-key id="UID">UID</translation-key> è un identificativo unico dell\'utente, generato attraverso le interazioni con <translation-key id="Borlabs-Cookie">Borlabs Cookie</translation-key>.','Backend / Consent Log / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key> stored.'=>'Non vengono memorizzati <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Log di consenso</translation-key>.','Backend / Consent Log / Headline<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Log di consenso</translation-key>','Backend / Consent Log / PlaceholderSearch UID...'=>'Cerca UID...','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineCookie Version'=>'Versione del cookie','Backend / Consent Log / Table Headline<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF Consent</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">Consenso TCF di IAB</translation-key>','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineService Consents'=>'Consensi per i servizi','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineStamp'=>'Data e ora','Backend / Consent Log / Table HeadlineUID'=>'UID','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / HeadlineClick on the icon to view details of the user\'s consents.'=>'Clicca sull\'icona per visualizzare i dettagli dei consensi dell\'utente.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Consent Logs</translation-key> show you the history of the user\'s consents. You can see which services the user has consented to and which not.'=>'I <translation-key id="Consent-Logs">Log di consenso</translation-key> mostrano la cronologia dei consensi dell\'utente. Puoi vedere a quali servizi l\'utente ha dato il proprio consenso e a quali no.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / TextDue to the volume of consent logs that can be accumulated, only consent logs from the past 7 days are displayed here. However, you can access older log entries by inputting the UID into the search field.'=>'A causa del volume dei log di consenso che possono essere accumulati, qui vengono visualizzati solo i log degli ultimi 7 giorni. Tuttavia, puoi accedere alle voci di log più vecchie inserendo l\'UID nel campo di ricerca.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / HeadlineWhat are Consent Logs?'=>'Cosa sono i log di consenso?','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / HeadlineSymbols explained'=>'Spiegazione dei simboli','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF Consent</translation-key>: The last consent has granted consent to the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> of the IAB TCF.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">Consenso TCF di IAB</translation-key>: l\'ultimo consenso è stato concesso ai <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Vendor</translation-key> del TCF di IAB.','Backend / Consent Log / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">IAB TCF Consent</translation-key>: The last consent did not granted consent to the <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Vendors</translation-key> of the IAB TCF.'=>'<translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Consent">Consenso TCF di IAB</translation-key>: l\'ultimo consenso non è stato concesso ai <translation-key id="IAB-TCF-Vendors">Vendor</translation-key> del TCF di IAB.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / BreadcrumbContent Blocker - Appearance'=>'Content blocker - Aspetto','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Label<translation-key id="Background-Color">Background Color</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Background-Color">Colore di sfondo</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelBorder Radius'=>'Raggio del bordo (border-radius)','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelBottom Left'=>'Inferiore sinistro','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelBottom Right'=>'Inferiore destro','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelButton'=>'Pulsante','Backend / Dialog Appearance / LabelButton Border Radius'=>'Raggio del bordo (border-radius) del pulsante','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelButton Color'=>'Colore del pulsante','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelButton Text Color'=>'Colore del testo del pulsante','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelContent Blocker'=>'Content blocker','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelDefault'=>'Predefinito','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelFont Family'=>'Famiglia caratteri (font-family)','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelFont Size (Base)'=>'Dimensione del carattere (base)','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelHover'=>'Hover','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelLink Color'=>'Colore del link','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelOpacity'=>'Trasparenza','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelSeparator Color'=>'Colore del separatore (separator)','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelSeparator Width'=>'Larghezza del separatore (separator)','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelText Color'=>'Colore del testo','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelTop Left'=>'Superiore sinistro','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / LabelTop Right'=>'Superiore destro','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HeadlineAppearance Settings'=>'Impostazioni di aspetto','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HeadlineReset Content Blocker Settings'=>'Ripristinare le impostazioni dei content blocker','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintDefines the visibility of the <translation-key id="Background-Color">Background Color</translation-key>.'=>'Definisce la visibilità del <translation-key id="Background-Color">Colore di sfondo</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintChoose which font you want to use. Your themes font is the default setting.'=>'Scegli il tipo di carattere che vuoi utilizzare. Il carattere del tuo tema è l\'impostazione predefinita.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintBased on the base font size, the font size of all elements are automatically adjusted proportionally.'=>'In base alla dimensione del carattere di base, la dimensione del carattere di tutti gli elementi viene automaticamente regolata in modo proporzionale.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / HintPlease confirm that you want to reset all <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content Blockers</translation-key> settings. They will be reset to their default settings.'=>'Conferma che desideri ripristinare tutte le impostazioni dei <translation-key id="Content-Blockers">Content blocker</translation-key>. Verranno ripristinate le impostazioni predefinite.','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Input PlaceholderEnter custom font family'=>'Inserisci la famiglia caratteri (font-family) personalizzata','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> Individual Settings'=>'Impostazioni individuali del <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> ','Backend / Content Blockers Appearance / Things to know / TextPlease note that the settings for <translation-key id="Button-Radius">Button Radius</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Button-Color">Button Color</translation-key>, and <translation-key id="Button-Text-Color">Button Text Color</translation-key> are often overwritten with the individual settings of a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Nota che le impostazioni di <translation-key id="Button-Radius">Raggio del pulsante</translation-key>, <translation-key id="Button-Color">Colore del pulsante</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Button-Text-Color">Colore del testo del pulsante</translation-key> sono spesso sovrascritte dalle impostazioni individuali di un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> selezionato non è disponibile nella lingua corrente.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> does not match the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> of the <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> selezionato non corrisponde al <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> del <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> selezionato non è disponibile nella lingua corrente.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> selezionato non esiste.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> does not exist.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> selezionato non esiste.','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageThe selected <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> is not available in the current language.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> selezionato non è disponibile nella lingua corrente.','Backend / Content Blockers / BreadcrumbEdit: {{ name }}'=>'Modificare: {{ name }}','Backend / Content Blockers / BreadcrumbContent Blockers'=>'Content blocker','Backend / Content Blockers / BreadcrumbNew'=>'Nuovo','Backend / Content Blockers / Button TitleApply Preset'=>'Applica la preimpostazione','Backend / Content Blockers / Button TitleSelect or Upload Image'=>'Seleziona o carica un\'immagine','Backend / Content Blockers / Button TitleUse this media'=>'Utilizza questo media','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelHost(s)'=>'Host','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelID'=>'ID','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelName'=>'Nome','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelPreset'=>'Preimpostazione','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Image</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Immagine</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelProvider List'=>'Elenco dei provider','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelService'=>'Servizio','Backend / Content Blockers / Label<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / LabelStatus'=>'Stato','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineAdditional Settings'=>'Impostazioni aggiuntive','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineContent Blocker Information'=>'Informazioni sul content blocker','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineContent Blocker Settings'=>'Impostazioni del content blocker','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineJavaScript'=>'JavaScript','Backend / Content Blockers / Headline<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Anteprima del contenuto bloccato</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineProvider Information'=>'Informazioni sul provider','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineService Information'=>'Informazioni sul servizio','Backend / Content Blockers / HintOnly use JavaScript, do not use <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong> tags!'=>'Utilizza solo JavaScript, non utilizzare tag <strong><em>&lt;script&gt;</em></strong>!','Backend / Content Blockers / Hint<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be set. The <translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> must be at least 3 characters long and may only contain: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>'=>'L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere impostato. L\'<translation-key id="ID">ID</translation-key> deve essere lungo almeno 3 caratteri e può contenere solo: <strong><em>a-z - _</em></strong>','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThe name of the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> which can be used within the <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> code by using the variable <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong>.'=>'Il nome del <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> che può essere usato all\'interno del codice <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Anteprima del contenuto bloccato</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> usando la variabile <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong>.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThis CSS will be used for the preview of the blocked content.'=>'Questo CSS verrà utilizzato per l\'anteprima del contenuto bloccato.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThis HTML will be used as the preview of the blocked content. You can use the following variables within the HTML code: <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong> to place the name of the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> and <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> to place the URL of the <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Image</translation-key>.'=>'Questo HTML verrà utilizzato come anteprima del contenuto bloccato. Puoi utilizzare le seguenti variabili all\'interno del codice HTML: <strong><em>{{ name }}</em></strong> per inserire il nome del <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> e <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> per inserire l\'URL dell\'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-Image">Immagine</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThis image is used as a preview for the blocked content (only with <translation-key id="Preset-B">Preset B</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Preset-C">Preset C</translation-key>). The URL of the image can be accessed within the <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> with the <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong> variable.'=>'Questa immagine viene utilizzata come anteprima del contenuto bloccato (solo con <translation-key id="Preset-B">Preimpostazione B</translation-key> e <translation-key id="Preset-C">Preimpostazione C</translation-key>). L\'URL dell\'immagine è accessibile all\'interno dell\'<translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Anteprima del contenuto bloccato</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> con la variabile <strong><em>{{ previewImage }}</em></strong>.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintUse this <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> if automatic detection does not work.'=>'Utilizza questo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> se il rilevamento automatico non funziona.','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThe status of this <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>. If enabled it does block content (iframes) of the configured <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key>.'=>'Lo stato di questo <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>. Se abilitato (stato: ON) blocca il contenuto (iframe) degli <translation-key id="Locations">Indirizzi</translation-key> configurati.','Backend / Content Blockers / OptionNo Service'=>'Nessun servizio','Backend / Content Blockers / OptionPreset A - Default'=>'Preimpostazione A - Predefinita','Backend / Content Blockers / Option<translation-key id="Preset-B">Preset B</translation-key> - Default + Background Image'=>'<translation-key id="Preset-B">Preimpostazione B</translation-key> - Immagine di sfondo predefinita','Backend / Content Blockers / Option<translation-key id="Preset-C">Preset C</translation-key> - Video Player'=>'<translation-key id="Preset-C">Preimpostazione C</translation-key> - Lettore video','Backend / Content Blockers / Input Placeholder...block this...'=>'...blocca questo...','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe code is executed in a function that uses the variable <strong><em>el</em></strong> as a parameter. <strong><em>el</em></strong> contains the unlocked object.'=>'Il codice viene eseguito in una funzione che utilizza la variabile <strong><em>el</em></strong> come parametro. <strong><em>el</em></strong> contiene l\'oggetto sbloccato.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / Code Examplefunction (contentBlockerData, el) { /* Here is your initialization code */ }'=>'Funzione (contentBlockerData, el) { /* Here is your initialization code */ }','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineFor Developers'=>'Per gli sviluppatori','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineGlobal JavaScript'=>'JavaScript Globale','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineInitialization JavaScript'=>'JavaScript Inizializzazione ','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> information?'=>'Qual è lo scopo delle informazioni sul <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>?','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> information?'=>'Qual è lo scopo delle informazioni sul <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key>?','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / Headline<translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> explained'=>'Spiegazione dello <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextJavaScript stored in the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field is executed once a blocked content is unblocked by the visitor (meaning only once per page). Use this, for example, to load an external JavaScript library.'=>'Il codice JavaScript memorizzato nel campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> viene eseguito una volta che un contenuto bloccato viene sbloccato dal visitatore (quindi solo una volta per pagina). Si può utilizzare, ad esempio, per caricare una libreria JavaScript esterna.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextTo execute the JavaScript stored in the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field before the blocked content is loaded, activate the option <translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Execute Global code before unblocking</translation-key>.'=>'Per eseguire il codice JavaScript memorizzato nel campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> prima che venga caricato il contenuto bloccato, attiva l\'opzione <translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Eseguire il codice Globale prima dello sblocco</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextIf this option is enabled and a visitor unblocks the content, the JavaScript from the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field will be executed before the blocked content is loaded.'=>'Se l\'opzione è attivata e un visitatore sblocca il contenuto, il JavaScript del campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> verrà eseguito prima del caricamento del contenuto bloccato.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / Code Examplefunction (contentBlockerData) { /* Here is your global code */ }'=>'Funzione (contentBlockerData) { /* Here is your global code */ }','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextJavaScript stored in the <translation-key id="Initialization">Initialization</translation-key> field is executed with every unblock of blocked content (meaning as many times as the visitor unblocks content). It is executed after the JavaScript from the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field.'=>'Il codice JavaScript memorizzato nel campo <translation-key id="Initialization">Inizializzazione</translation-key> viene eseguito a ogni sblocco del contenuto bloccato (cioè tante volte quanto il visitatore sblocca il contenuto). Viene eseguito dopo il JavaScript del campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextFor legal compliance, every <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> must be linked to a specific <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.'=>'Per motivi di conformità legale, ogni <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> deve essere collegato a un <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> specifico.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextIn the <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> section (found under <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Consent Management</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Providers</translation-key>), you will find more information and also have the option to edit or create new <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> entries.'=>'Nella sezione <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key> (che si trova sotto <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management">Gestione consenso</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Navigation-Consent-Management-Providers">Provider</translation-key>), troverai ulteriori informazioni e avrai anche la possibilità di modificare o creare nuove voci <translation-key id="Provider">Provider</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextIt\'s optional, but there are two good reasons why you should link a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> to a specific <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'È facoltativo, ma ci sono due buoni motivi per collegare un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> a un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> specifico.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextLinking a <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> to a <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> enables automatic unblocking of content for visitors upon granting consent to the  <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key> through the <translation-key id="Dialog">Dialog</translation-key>.'=>'Il collegamento di un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> a un <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> consente di sbloccare automaticamente i contenuti per i visitatori dopo aver concesso il consenso al <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> attraverso la <translation-key id="Dialog">Finestra di dialogo</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextYou can extend the information about the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, for example with cookie information, via the linked <translation-key id="Service">Service</translation-key>.'=>'Puoi ampliare le informazioni sul <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, ad esempio con informazioni sui cookie, tramite il <translation-key id="Service">Servizio</translation-key> collegato.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextUse the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to block content that is not automatically blocked. If contents use the oEmbed format, for example <strong>Pinterest</strong> links, use the <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> to avoid display errors and block the content: {{ shortcode }}'=>'Utilizza lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> per bloccare i contenuti che non vengono bloccati automaticamente. Se i contenuti utilizzano il formato oEmbed, ad esempio i link di <strong>Pinterest</strong>, utilizza lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> per evitare errori di visualizzazione e bloccare il contenuto: {{ shortcode }}}.','Backend / Content Blockers / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> is not available until the <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> is created.'=>'Lo <translation-key id="Shortcode">Shortcode</translation-key> non è disponibile finché non viene creato il <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Content Blocker / Label<translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Execute Global code before unblocking</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Execute-Global-code-before-unblocking">Eseguire il codice Globale prima dello sblocco</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker / HintIf this option is enabled and a visitor unblocks the content, the JavaScript in the <translation-key id="Global">Global</translation-key> field will be executed before the blocked content is loaded.'=>'Se questa opzione è attivata (stato: ON) e un visitatore sblocca il contenuto, il JavaScript nel campo <translation-key id="Global">Globale</translation-key> verrà eseguito prima del caricamento del contenuto bloccato.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Testo segnaposto</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / ButtonAdd Text Placeholder'=>'Aggiungi un testo segnaposto','Backend / Content Blocker Host / LabelKey'=>'Chiave','Backend / Content Blocker Host / LabelText'=>'Testo','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Headline<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Testo segnaposto</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Table Headline<translation-key id="Key">Key</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Key">Chiave</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Table Headline<translation-key id="Text">Text</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Text">Testo</translation-key>','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Testo segnaposto</translation-key>?','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Things to know / Text<translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Text Placeholder</translation-key> facilitates the creation of text placeholders for your <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>, streamlining your text adjustment process.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Text-Placeholder">Testo segnaposto</translation-key> facilita la creazione di un testo segnaposto per il <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>, semplificando il processo di regolazione del testo.','Backend / Content Blocker Language String / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Key">Key</translation-key> you specify can be placed in your <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Preview Blocked Content</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> code using the <strong><em>{{ yourKey }}</em></strong> variable. It will be automatically replaced by the text specified in the <translation-key id="Text">Text</translation-key> field when the content is blocked.'=>'La <translation-key id="Key">Chiave</translation-key> che hai specificato può essere inserita nel codice <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content">Anteprima del contenuto bloccato</translation-key> &raquo; <translation-key id="Preview-Blocked-Content-HTML">HTML</translation-key> utilizzando la variabile <strong><em>{{ tuaChiave }}</em></strong>. Verrà automaticamente sostituito dal testo specificato nel campo <translation-key id="Text">Testo</translation-key> quando il contenuto viene bloccato.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Location">Location</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Location">Indirizzo</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / ButtonAdd Location'=>'Aggiungi un indirizzo','Backend / Content Blocker Location / LabelHostname'=>'Nome host','Backend / Content Blocker Location / LabelPath'=>'Percorso','Backend / Content Blocker Location / HeadlineLocations'=>'Indirizzi','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Table Headline<translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key>','Backend / API Client / AlertThe scan quota has been exceeded. Please try again later.'=>'La quota di scansione è stata superata. Riprovare più tardi.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Table Headline<translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key>'=>'<translation-key id="Path">Percorso</translation-key>','Backend / API Client / AlertThe maximum number of pages to scan has been exceeded. Please try again later.'=>'È stato superato il numero massimo di pagine da scansionare. Riprovare più tardi.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key>?'=>'Che cos\'è un <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key>?','Backend / API Client / AlertThe request could not be authorized. Please try again later.'=>'La richiesta non è stata autorizzata. Si prega di riprovare più tardi.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Things to know / HeadlineWhat is the purpose of the <translation-key id="Locations">Locations</translation-key> section?'=>'Qual è lo scopo della sezione <translation-key id="Locations">Indirizzi</translation-key>?','Backend / API Client / AlertThe request could not be validated. Please try again later.'=>'Non è stato possibile convalidare la richiesta. Riprovare più tardi.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Things to know / TextThe <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is the domain name of the website. For example, if the URL of the website is <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, the <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> is <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.'=>'Il <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key> è il nome di dominio del sito web. Ad esempio, se l\'URL del sito web è <strong><em>https://www.example.com</em></strong>, il <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key> è <strong><em>www.example.com</em></strong>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertAn error occurred while communicating with the Borlabs Cloud API. Please try again later.'=>'Si è verificato un errore durante la comunicazione con l\'API di Borlabs Cloud. Riprovare più tardi.','Backend / Content Blocker Location / Things to know / TextIf a <translation-key id="Hostname">Hostname</translation-key> and <translation-key id="Path">Path</translation-key> configured here are found in an iframe, the iframe is blocked with the settings of this <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key>.'=>'Se un <translation-key id="Hostname">Nome host</translation-key> e un <translation-key id="Path">Percorso</translation-key> configurati qui vengono trovati in un iframe, l\'iframe viene bloccato con le impostazioni di questo <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key>.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertConnectivity problem'=>'Problema di connessione','Backend / Content Blockers / Alert MessageNo <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> configured.'=>'Nessun <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> configurato.','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertName could not be resolved'=>'Impossibile risolvere il nome','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertNo answer from scanner'=>'Nessuna risposta dallo scanner','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertOther problem'=>'Altro problema','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineContent Blockers'=>'Content blocker','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertSSL error'=>'Errore SSL','Backend / Content Blockers / HeadlineReset Content Blockers'=>'Ripristinare i content blocker','Backend / Cloud Scan / AlertTimeout'=>'Timeout','Backend / Content Blockers / HintThe <translation-key id="ContentBlockerDefault">Content Blocker: <em>Default</em></translation-key> is used for all external contents, for which no own <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content Blocker</translation-key> was created.'=>'Il <translation-key id="ContentBlockerDefault">Content blocker: <em>Predefinito</em></translation-key> viene utilizzato per tutti i contenuti esterni per i quali non è stato creato un <translation-key id="Content-Blocker">Content blocker</translation-key> proprio.